import './App.css';
import { ChakraProvider,Box ,Container,Flex,CSSReset,GridItem,Grid,Text} from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { } from '@chakra-ui/icons'
import Navbar from './components/navBar';
import SideBar from './components/leftSideBar';


function App() {
  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <CSSReset />
      <Flex direction="column" height="100vh" bgColor='#F7F7F8'>
        <Navbar />
        <Flex flex="1">
          {/* Adjust the Box styling as needed */}
          <Box
          
            width="100%"
            mx='2'
            my='2'
            align="center"
            justify="center"
          >
            <Grid templateColumns="13% 62% 25%"  h="100%" w='100%'>
              <GridItem colSpan={1} borderLeftRadius='20' bgColor="gray" mr='2' >
                <Box>
                <Container mt='5'>
                <Text> List chat history </Text>
                </Container>
                
               </Box>
              </GridItem>
              <GridItem colSpan={1}  bgColor="#F7F7F8">
              <Box>
                <Container mt='5' bgColor={'#646464'} maxW='full' h='100px'>
                  <Text> New chat room </Text>
                </Container>



               </Box>
              </GridItem>
              <GridItem colSpan={1} borderRightRadius='20' bgColor="gray" ml='2'>
              <Box>
                <Container mt='5'>
                List chat history
                </Container>
               </Box>
              </GridItem>
            </Grid>
          </Box>
        </Flex>
      </Flex>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
}

export default App;
